<section class="hero is-medium has-text-centered"> 
  @Html.Partial("_header")  
</section>

<hr class="is-marginless">

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h3 class="title is-2">
      <span class="icon is-medium">
          <i class="fa fa-th-large"></i>
        </span>
        The Jansen/Cabrita<strong> family</strong>
    </h3>
    <h4 class="subtitle is-4">A Dutch - Portuguese collaboration</h4>
    <div class="tile is-ancestor">
      <div class="tile is-vertical is-8">
        <div class="tile">
          <div class="tile is-parent is-vertical">
            <article class="tile is-child notification is-morningsky">
              <p class="title">Where</p>
              <p class="subtitle">                
                We live in Holland in the city of Delft.
              </p>
              <figure class="image is-4by4">                
                <img src="@Context.GetLink("/img/delft.jpg")">
              </figure>
            </article>
            <article class="tile is-child notification is-honey">
              <p class="title">What</p>
              <p class="subtitle">We have four people and a cat in our family.</p>
              <div class="content">
                <p>Bas is from Holland, Guida is from Portugal and the boys are born in Holland.</p>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
          <div class="tile is-parent">
            <article class="tile is-child notification is-cerulean">
              <p class="title">Who</p>
              <p class="subtitle">This is who we are</p>
              <figure class="image is-4by4">                
                <img src="@Context.GetLink("/img/emiliotomas.jpg")">
              </figure>
              <div class="content">
                <ul>
                <li>Bas Jansen, the dad</li>
                <li>Ana Cabrita also known as Guida, the mom</li>
                <li>Tomas Jansen, the oldest son</li>
                <li>Emilio Jansen, the youngest</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tile is-parent">
          <article class="tile is-child notification is-morningsky">
            <p class="title">Why</p>
            <p class="subtitle">We just want to let you know who we are and where we live and how to contact us.</p>
            <div class="content">
              <p>So if you want contact us send an email to bas or guida @@hipsville.com.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tile is-parent">
        <article class="tile is-child notification is-mist">
          <p class="title">When</p>
          <p class="subtitle">It started in 2008</p>
          <div class="content">
            <p>It started in 2007 when Guida en Bas met at a winter bbq. It did not work out that night but a few month later we met again and never were apart since.</p>
            <p>In 2008 Tomas was born on Oosteinde 47.</p>
            <p>In 2011 Emilio was born also on the Oostsingel soon after we moved to our new house Oostsingel and lived there ever since. Nina our cat joint us a little later.</p>
          </div>
          <figure class="image is-4by4">                
             <img src="@Context.GetLink("/img/guida.jpg")">
          </figure>
          <div class="content">
            <p></p>            
          </div>
          <figure class="image is-4by4">                
             <img src="@Context.GetLink("/img/bas.jpg")">
          </figure>
          
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


